flowRoot.flowPara: は の に い︒
as waves rise, they are lifted,
O smitch o siller, sea speugie.
As jaws heize up, they heize up,
As the jaws pu oot, blinkin scarras.
O smitch o siller, sea speugie..
as a wee het airn gleed,
